studyArms.name: Nasal Glucagon (LY900018)
studyArms.description: Single 3-mg dose of nasal glucagon powder administered by study site personnel using a single-use nasal dosing device.

studyArms.name: Intramuscular Glucagon (IMG)
studyArms.description: Single 1-mg dose of GlucaGen administered by intramuscular injection by study site personnel following reconstitution.

studyCohorts.name: Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus (T1DM)

studyCohorts.characteristic: Japanese patients with T2DM on daily insulin therapy for at least 1 year.
